### 2.7 Ralph Workflow Alignment

| Ralph Principle | Front-End Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Modularity** | Feature-Sliced Design prevents feature coupling; each feature is independently deployable as a module |
| **Deployment Readiness** | Environment config via `.env.local`; `next.config.js` uses `output: 'standalone'` for Docker; Vercel `vercel.json` defines region pinning |
| **Stateless Handoffs** | All agent-delegated components are self-contained with their own data hooks; no prop-drilling across feature boundaries |
| **Documented Contracts** | Each `features/*/index.ts` exports a typed public API; consumers may not reach into internal files |
| **Task Registry** | Each new component created by an agent is logged in `.agent/docs/task-registry.md` |

